{"tid":658524,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"身邊啲朋友整晒容...變晒大陸雞。","createTime":"2018-05-09T05:08:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-09T12:35:37.000Z","uid":185736,"like":29,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"5ee915c7600dc99d440a4966073da3081b53a11a","tid":658524,"uid":185736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T05:08:30.000Z","msg":"中學玩開嗰堆依家個個大個女，走晒上大陸整容... <br />\n大眼 縮鼻 高鼻 瘦面... 就嚟全部都一樣樣喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見到中同啲朋友都整到勁誇張，好醜怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n次次見到佢地po相，個心都係出一句。<br />\n「不求同年同月同日生，但求同眼同鼻同醫生。」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢地個樣同呢啲差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/09/125514_f76e0c1d2f7e18f17ef31c8479a8b992.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F09%2F125514_f76e0c1d2f7e18f17ef31c8479a8b992.png&h=fd10252e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我真係唔知邊個係nana喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好想嚾佢唔好整...佢依家又話想去整瘦面喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f320cb7aa30d99559084a1af97a0bc67156eccb1","tid":658524,"uid":77569,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T05:13:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d2e8c2dd4aa8154cbf34d973a23e58f63454d05b","tid":658524,"uid":85659,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T05:13:06.000Z","msg":"見面個陣 大叫:「叫NANA既企起身」咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15dd7490a25796dda748468a4882850bee3b6ff5","tid":658524,"uid":57835,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T05:13:43.000Z","msg":"張相好誇張喎"},{"pid":"441b4a17a926af18eb06c7718813d5588b4dd5b9","tid":658524,"uid":10249,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"